info.name: novajoin
info.summary: Nova integration to enroll IPA clients

vulnerabilities.details: A flaw was discovered in the python-novajoin plugin, all versions up to, excluding 1.1.1, for Red Hat OpenStack Platform. The novajoin API lacked sufficient access control, allowing any keystone authenticated user to generate FreeIPA tokens.
